{"tid":52124,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對男友好失望 又好唔開心。","createTime":"2016-12-23T19:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T20:26:33.000Z","uid":21189,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2be045ca83cbba1a7d692793bacaaa6e9f9be1f","tid":52124,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:11:19.000Z","msg":"一直以來同男友相處都好好 好恩愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇咩問題  但前兩日因為小事吵左<br />\n係因為佢應承左我一啲小事做唔到<br />\n我個人好重視承諾 覺得應承左就要做<br />\n跟住冷戰左一日 佢冇點氹我 只係搵左我一兩次<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢頭先搵返我 <br />\n同我講佢噚日原來返工整親受傷入左醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢噚日冇同我講 <br />\n我係最後一個知 <br />\n我真係好唔開心好失望 <br />\n點解佢有事唔係即刻同我講 <br />\n係最後先話我知<br />\n如果佢同我講我會即刻飛去醫師睇佢<br />\n佢話驚我未嬲完會覺得佢係搏同情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係我冇重要到可以同佢分擔所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直以為我對佢好重要 佢對我都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc47043f4126acedeb4dce20eaadc9eb0a965ec4","tid":52124,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！"},{"pid":"978394ae3edcfeaddff2632a25d40e677397edb9","tid":52124,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6937eb2813b18bc3b2411096f5bc89aacdb8705","tid":52124,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你確定你男朋友同你價值觀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1653da43e7d317fac84ffa1006257c1ec8ddb232","tid":52124,"uid":23115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:20:21.000Z","msg":"失咩望...<br />\n不如諗下點解佢有呢啲行為?<br />\n<br />\n唔同你講一係怕你擔心二係你對佢發完惡點感搵你住呢<br />\n正常架<br />\n<br />\n咁又小題大造去失望去唔開心<br />\n個世界就好似圍住你轉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cca3c3b970ee356bfd78468eaa17e569646daf","tid":52124,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你確定你男朋友同你價值觀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢話驚我覺得佢扮野所以唔講...聽完真心灰左"},{"pid":"f1a091db656ee909bc4dc8d80934a68575a92f97","tid":52124,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你同佢又冷戰緊<br />\n有時想搵你都唔知點開口啦<br />\n<br />\n嘈咩都好，永遠記住唔好過夜<br />\n最多最多去到第二朝就要回復返正常<br />\n唔好話鬥氣邊個要搵邊個先<br />\n為左啖氣，傷左感情，無謂嘛"},{"pid":"e4bd1179995ab222cd0360e30953b4e62ea17e46","tid":52124,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你確定你男朋友同你價值觀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢話驚我覺得佢扮野所以唔講...聽完真心灰左</blockquote><br />\n你既然都唔知 點可以淨係用自己果套去諗對方<br />\n對方根本未必係你咁諗"},{"pid":"2647985b87f60804b68f22c4d66eaacd34d34c8f","tid":52124,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19