"2016-12-23T19:24:11.000Z","msg":"你男友係真男人,完。<br />\n係一個你嬲緊既情況下,未諗到計氹你仲要你反安慰?點知你仲可以理解成最後一個講,今鋪輸清光,sorry for1999,不過如果唔係你嬲緊既情況下你覺得佢會第幾個通知你?唔洗答我自己諗完自己反思。"},{"pid":"f4108303bb07c4c1af4d6501e848f4b2a01ae65e","tid":52124,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你確定你男朋友同你價值觀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢話驚我覺得佢扮野所以唔講...聽完真心灰左</blockquote><br />\n你既然都唔知 點可以淨係用自己果套去諗對方<br />\n對方根本未必係你咁諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心<br />\n多啲溝通<br />\n<br />\n深層次既溝通呀<br />\n討論下大家既價值觀，對唔同事情既睇法<br />\n平時有咩野唔好收埋收埋唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n多啲問下對方既意見，少啲發脾氣"},{"pid":"3eeec566ef73ca77e90d8b631a3be3ddaff11c8a","tid":52124,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:25:53.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯<br />\n你諗太多<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"5305d1192b5a6bc5de758561669264cf999d8877","tid":52124,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你確定你男朋友同你價值觀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢話驚我覺得佢扮野所以唔講...聽完真心灰左</blockquote><br />\n你既然都唔知 點可以淨係用自己果套去諗對方<br />\n對方根本未必係你咁諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然你男朋友對你咁重要，點解唔可以相信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔想利用你嘅擔心同可憐黎原諒佢，其實係男人尊嚴既一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf50b5d6df17a5f0bbdef5574003b0c717417ef","tid":52124,"uid":10100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:27:40.000Z","msg":"人地工傷仲要俾你嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e187c5bbfaba52ea6ebbcd9ab7a70fcfdc07ee1","tid":52124,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想你擔心嘛，蠢豬！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊唔係應該所有野都一齊分擔一齊分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你同佢又冷戰緊<br />\n有時想搵你都唔知點開口啦<br />\n<br />\n嘈咩都好，永遠記住唔好過夜<br />\n最多最多去到第二朝就要回復返正常<br />\n唔好話鬥氣邊個要搵邊個先<br />\n為左啖氣，傷左感情，無謂嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但咁大件事都應該同我講聲掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似外人咁 自己男友有事自己反而唔知<br />\n<br />\n平時都好小冷戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多嘈兩句轉頭就冇事...</blockquote><br />\n咁你就唔好為左啲小事嘈佢咁耐啦 on9 <br />\n俾返個下台階佢好下台嘛<br />\n下下頂到咁恆，俾我都唔理你啦，仲要冷戰<br />\n<br />\n佢承諾左你做唔到，咁你咪俾多次機會佢<br />\n又或者你罰佢囉<br />\n罰佢要整野食俾你又好，買杯雪糕俾你又好<br />\n再要佢自己保証以後承諾左要做得到<br />\n咪得囉！女人呀！<br />\n<br />\n唔係剩係男人要面架<br />\n全地球人都要面架<br />\n我宜家唔係教緊你拍拖<br />\n我教緊你做人呀，呀女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1aeaba90232043f586f0d88818116c3bae845b","tid":52124,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你既然都唔知 點可以淨係用自己果套去諗對方<br />\n對方根本未必係你咁諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然你男朋友對你咁重要，點解唔可以相信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔想利用你嘅擔心同可憐黎原諒佢，